
# Utility Application Architecture Diagram (Hostinger + Render)

> **Note:** To view the diagram below, install a Mermaid preview extension in VS Code (such as "Markdown Preview Mermaid Support").

## Architecture & Data Flow

- **Frontend (React):** Deployed on Hostinger, serves UI components (e.g., Template Management, PDF Generator, Public Catalog).
- **Backend (Spring Boot):** Deployed on Render, exposes REST APIs for frontend, business logic, and database access.
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (managed by Render), stores application data (templates, users, PDFs, etc).


```mermaid
flowchart TD
	subgraph Hostinger
		FE_TM["Template Management (UI)"]
		FE_PDF["PDF Generator (UI)"]
		FE_PC["Public Catalog (UI)"]
	end
	subgraph Render
		BE_TM["Template Service (REST API)"]
		BE_PDF["PDF Service (REST API)"]
		BE_PC["Catalog Service (REST API)"]
		DB_TEMPLATES[("templates table")]
		DB_USERS[("users table")]
		DB_PDFS[("pdfs table")]
	end
	FE_TM -- "CRUD API calls" --> BE_TM
	FE_PDF -- "Generate PDF API" --> BE_PDF
	FE_PC -- "Catalog API" --> BE_PC
	BE_TM -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_TEMPLATES
	BE_TM -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_USERS
	BE_PDF -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_PDFS
	BE_PDF -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_TEMPLATES
	BE_PC -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_TEMPLATES
	BE_PC -- "ORM/JDBC" --> DB_PDFS
```


### End-to-End Flow by Feature

#### 1. Template Management
- **UI:** Template Management (React on Hostinger)
- **Backend:** Template Service (Spring Boot on Render)
- **DB:** templates, users tables

#### 2. PDF Generator
- **UI:** PDF Generator (React on Hostinger)
- **Backend:** PDF Service (Spring Boot on Render)
- **DB:** pdfs, templates tables

#### 3. Public Catalog
- **UI:** Public Catalog (React on Hostinger)
- **Backend:** Catalog Service (Spring Boot on Render)
- **DB:** templates, pdfs tables

